Class TerminalConnectionListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.CallListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.ConnectionListenerAdapter
        • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.TerminalConnectionListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, CallListener, ConnectionListener, TerminalConnectionListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CallControlTerminalConnectionListenerAdapter

    public class TerminalConnectionListenerAdapter
extends ConnectionListenerAdapter
implements TerminalConnectionListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to the TerminalConnection object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    TerminalConnectionListener
